title: Killeen High School
text:
Killeen High School is a 6A <a href="public%20high%20school">public high school</a> located in <a href="Killeen%2C%20Texas">Killeen</a>, <a href="Texas">Texas</a> (<a href="United%20States">USA</a>). It is one of 7 high schools in the <a href="Killeen%20Independent%20School%20District">Killeen Independent School District</a> located in western <a href="Bell%20County%2C%20Texas">Bell County</a>. In 2011, the school was rated "<a href="Texas%20Education%20Agency%20accountability%20ratings%20system">Academically Acceptable</a>" by the <a href="Texas%20Education%20Agency">Texas Education Agency</a>.
